===Noun===
'''[[kissing]] [[gourami]]'''
#''[[Helostoma temminckii]]'', a large tropical [[freshwater]] [[fish]]. They are commercial food fish which are farmed in their native [[Southeast Asia]], and are also popular with [[aquarium|aquarists]] for the fish's peculiar "[[kissing]]" behaviour.
